---
title: American Pork Rissoles & BBQ Relish with Rosemary Kumara Wedges
description: Rissoles, that classic family staple, get a dash of sweetness with a coating of sticky BBQ relish. With rosemary-infused kumara wedges and a fresh garden salad, this meal shines a whole new light on a tried-and-true dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/american-pork-rissoles-bbq-relish-64af9b88.jpg
